## In-phase drop-in requests

When the user requests a change during the **current** phase (UX tweak, extra acceptance criterion, etc.):

1. Update that phase’s `specs/…-phaseN-slug/` (`requirements.html`, `validation.html`, `plan.html`/`index.html` as needed) in the **same** work session as the code.
2. Add a row to **Phase amendments** in `requirements.html`.
3. Follow `specs/validation-policy.html#in-phase-amendments` and `productizer-phase-spec`.
4. Do not expand into the next roadmap phase without explicit approval.
